        <updateDate>2020-03-25T16:22:20Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Telework Metrics and Cost Savings Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires a federal agency's telework policy to include information on (1) annual goals for increasing the telework participation rate, and (2) methods for collecting data related to cost savings achieved through telework.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
